This comprehensive exploration shows that CitedBy.ai uses a **simple, localStorage-based architecture** with:
- Central state management in App.tsx
- Analysis results stored as AnalysisResult objects
- Pre-populated tool pages based on URL history
- Independent credit/generation systems per tool
